name: Peach Vision
description: Everything faded turn to pitch black. He had a hard time remembering just what the hell happened last night. He wasn't sure of downing some random pills from of the medicine cabinet, his first attempt on everything. Making sure he would not recover, if the pills didn't do the job, he had already devised the set up of the nonsense in his bedroom. Definitely, he didn't recall anyone cutting the rope, forcing him down to the floor.
